      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Problem Statement"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Small business owners and online entrepreneurs are leaving hundreds of thousands of dollars in business credit and funding on the table because they don't know the right process, lenders, or order of operations. Banks reject them. The SBA process is confusing. Predatory lenders charge 40%+ APR. Funded First cuts through the noise with a step-by-step system for building fundable business credit and accessing capital at favorable terms."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Goals"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Guide users from zero business credit to $50K\u2013$500K in funding within 12 months"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Demystify business credit scoring, vendor accounts, and lender requirements"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Provide a self-paced program with AI-powered coaching and document templates"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Build a referral flywheel where funded customers refer others"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
